City: prague, edinburgh
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Hobby       | traveling | board-games |
| City         | prague      | edinburgh  |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike   |

